title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1989-12-31
description:
Set 1

Sugar Magnolia, Touch Of Gray, Women Are Smarter, Big Boss Man*, Memphis Blues, Shakedown Street

Set 2

Iko Iko, Victim Or The Crime-> Dark Star-> Drums-> Jam-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Throwing Stones, Not Fade Away

Set 3

Brokedown Palace, Sunshine Daydream, E: Midnight Hour

*with Bonnie Raitt, slide guitar
